accessories.title: Ninebot Engine Speaker
accessories.description: The built-in engine sound simulation system can simulate the realistic engine roar based on the vehicle accelerator, brake, speed, and other signals

accessories.title: Extension Rod
accessories.description: The Extension Rod helps you to easily maneuver your scooter, so you no longer need to bend over and push it, making it easier to take with you anywhere.

accessories.title: Segway Protective Gear Set
accessories.description: The curved, streamlined design of the helmet shell, coupled with the thick, high-quality fabrics create a helmet that is stylish, protective and comfortable to wear.

accessories.title: Ninebot Leisure Backpack
accessories.description: The Ninebot leisure backpack adopts a stylish gray-yellow color contrast, adding a trendy accessory to your wardrobe.

accessories.title: Segway External Battery
accessories.description: It is easy to install and increases the range of the ES1, ES2 & E22 to 27.9, 28 and 27 miles respectively and It also increases the speed

accessories.title: Segway Charger
accessories.description: Whether at home, the office, or on your KickScooter journey, this Ninebot KickScooter by Segway Charger is designed to provide a safe and stable charge anytime, anywhere.

accessories.title: Segway Scooter Bag
accessories.description: Whether at home, the office, or on your KickScooter journey, this Ninebot KickScooter by Segway Charger is designed to provide a safe and stable charge anytime, anywhere.

accessories.title: Segway Phone Holder
accessories.description: The dual screw, non-slip design offers ultimate security and versatility. The phone holder is applicable to multiple vehicle series.

accessories.title: Segway Saddle
accessories.description: This scooter seat is designed to work with the MAX. It offers high quality, comfort and safety that is in line with the MAX KickScooter.
